headline: Cisco’s Secure AI Factory Links Sovereign Data Push To Valuation Story
summary: Cisco Systems launched Australia's first Secure AI Factory in partnership with SharonAI Holdings and NVIDIA. The project focuses on sovereign AI infrastructure, keeping AI data processing within Australia. The Secure AI Factory is designed to support secure, high performance AI workloads for Australian customers.
